optional (if needed in your system):
   * install "tensorflow object detector api"
      1st: done t3-si requirements.txt
         - your tensorflow is installed in ~/.local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow
      2nd: install more packages
         - $ sudo apt-get install protobuf-compiler python-pil python-lxml python-tk
         - $ pip install Cython
      3rd: $ cd ~/.local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow
           $ git clone https://github.com/tensorflow/models.git
      4th: $ cd models/research
           $ protoc object_detection/protos/*.proto --python_out=.
      5th: modify PYTHONPATH in ~/.bashrc ... add two paths ...
           $HOME/.local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow/models/research
           $HOME/.local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow/models/research/slim
